steal your heart. It has the shape of Kurinji flowers which is the attraction of Rajamala, Idukki, and Kerala. Your eyes and mind glitter like the petals of the Haarlu when you visit the most amazing place on earth.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2a1fd3b elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"2a1fd3b\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"819\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https:\/\/rivermistresorts.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/Devaramane-Hills-Mist-819x1024.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-5398\" alt=\"Devaramane Hills Mist\" srcset=\"https:\/\/rivermistresorts.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/Devaramane-Hills-Mist-819x1024.jpg 819w, https:\/\/rivermistresorts.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/Devaramane-Hills-Mist-240x300.jpg 240w, https:\/\/rivermistresorts.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/Devaramane-Hills-Mist-768x960.jpg 768w, https:\/\/rivermistresorts.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/Devaramane-Hills-Mist.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 819px) 100vw, 819px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2a4103c elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"2a4103c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Image Credit: <a href=\"https:\/\/www.instagram.com\/talkies_winter\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Winter Talkies<\/a><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4af4ce6 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"4af4ce6\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"