ement elementor-element-88e861b elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"88e861b\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"960\" height=\"1001\" src=\"https:\/\/rivermistresorts.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/Kalabhairaveshwara-Temple.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-5402\" alt=\"Kalabhairaveshwara Temple\" srcset=\"https:\/\/rivermistresorts.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/Kalabhairaveshwara-Temple.jpg 960w, https:\/\/rivermistresorts.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/Kalabhairaveshwara-Temple-288x300.jpg 288w, https:\/\/rivermistresorts.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/Kalabhairaveshwara-Temple-768x801.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-91cd0fe elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"91cd0fe\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Each journey is a spiritual search. India&#8217;s rich culture honestly agrees with this philosophy. There is a dislocated historical temple popularly known as the Kalabhairaveshwara temple.<\/p><p><span style=\"font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; font-style: var(--fontStyle, inherit); letter-spacing: var(--letterSpacing); text-transform: var(--textTransform);\">This 800-year-old historical temple is also quite popular among the locals by the name of \u2018Mane Devru\u2019. The temple is protected with dignity as it is closely related to the daily life of the locals. It is about 2-3 kilometers towards Mudigere from Kottigehara and according to the signboard, one needs to take a right turn and then travel twelve kilometers to reach the place.<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8e617c3 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"8e617c3\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">An aww-mazing place without a second thought<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-fb376c4 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"fb376c4\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" src=\"https:\/\/rivermistresorts.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/Devaramane-Hills-Sunset-View-1024x576.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-5405\" alt=\"Devaramane Hills Sunset View from top\" srcset=\"https:\/\/rivermistresorts.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/Devaramane-Hills-Sunset-View-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/rivermistresorts.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/Devaramane-Hills-Sunset-View-300x169.jpg 300w, https:\/\/rivermistresorts.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/Devaramane-Hills-Sunset-View-768x432.jpg 768w, https:\/\/rivermistresorts.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/Devaramane-Hills-Sunset-View.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0164248 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"0164248\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Image Credit: <a href=\"https:\/\/www.instagram.com\/manju_chasingviews\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Manjunath Krishnamurthy<\/a><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t