default\">The aura of chikmagalur and devaramane hills<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c0a97e4 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"c0a97e4\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" src=\"https:\/\/rivermistresorts.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/devaramane-hills-chikmagalur-1024x576.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-5412\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/rivermistresorts.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/devaramane-hills-chikmagalur-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/rivermistresorts.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/devaramane-hills-chikmagalur-300x169.jpg 300w, https:\/\/rivermistresorts.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/devaramane-hills-chikmagalur-768x432.jpg 768w, https:\/\/rivermistresorts.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/devaramane-hills-chikmagalur.jpg 1040w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6a458df elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"6a458df\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Devaramane is the centre of attraction for nature lovers. You can see a new world around you when you are walking through the greenery, when you touch the drops of the river flowing between the hills, the misty surroundings, and the aura of Chikmagalur.\u00a0<\/p><p>Hailu is a unique purple flower that blooms once every twelve years and gives the hills a cushioned and carpeted appearance. The Devaramane hills are located in the Gutti village which creates a close connection between man and nature. It is a visual treat for everyone and your mind will touch the core of your heart with the beauty.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5f8c431 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"5f8c431\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Heavenly experience of a beautiful getaway\n<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ba48934 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"ba48934\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https:\/\/rivermistresorts.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/Devaramane-betta-top-1024x1024.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-5418\" alt=\"Devaramane betta top view after trekking\" srcset=\"https:\/\/rivermistresorts.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/Devaramane-betta-top-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/rivermistresorts.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/Devaramane-betta-top-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/rivermistresorts.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/Devaramane-betta-top-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/rivermistresorts.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/Devaramane-betta-top-768x768.jpg 768w, https:\/\/rivermistresorts.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/Devaramane-betta-top.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-af256e5 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"af256e5\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Image Credit: <a href=\"https:\/\/www.instagram.com